data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Discover the comfort of modern living in this 3bd, 2 bath Home just moments from Town near City Park & Chemeketa CC. Quiet neighborhood in a Cul-De-Sac street with little traffic. AC is an added bonus & bedrooms provide comfort and flexibility, with the convenience of a jack & jill bathroom in the Primary bedroom. Back patio off living area, Property features UG sprinklers, a large attached 2-car garage, & RV Pad! Most appliances are newer, as well as carpet throughout the home. Call/Text Billy 541-619-1632
